ar's book i despair servant fates series added short stories downloadable content nearly year after release this current form not monetised similar form updates for pc games see also cloud gaming references giskard total annihilation rtsg classic engineering guild retrieved total annihilation was one early adopters dlc releases every month cavedog would release new unit for free try with game ta downloadable units on cavedogcom archived internet archive on march gamesindustrybiz sony confirms ps2 online plans theregistercouk retrieved goldstein hilary ninja gaiden hurricane pack vol q&a - new details on enemies ai changes camera fixes exclusive screens show off even more enemies second costume retrieved sterling jim march oblivion's horse armor dlc still selling destructoid retrieved horse armor downloadable content for elder scrolls iv oblivion has become notorious premier example bad dlc it's pointless waste money that gives something totally useful non-character you'll barely use gran turismo hd will be barebones release videogamercom retrieved guitar hero ii for xbox have most dlc ever videogamercom retrieved rock band expensive hobby but how expensive rockbandaidecom retrieved ign picross ds retrieved 1up picross ds review retrieved professor layton not so downloadable content retrieved first 3ds game with paid dlc theatrhythm final fantasy chen brian x apple allows in-app purchases free iphone apps wired retrieved martin robinson molyneux $50000 curiosity dlc nothing be ashamed eurogamer retrieved chris morrison popular facebook game enrages players by adding micro-transactions venturebeat retrieved ransom-wiley james download oblivion's horse armor for price joystiq retrieved raumer daniel electronic arts - …kämpft gegen gebrauchte spiele gamestar idg retrieved adam satariano cliff edwards electronic arts lost alien landscape businessweekcom retrieved project ten dollar coupon program reward people who purchase new game with downloadable content upgrades peop